name: RE-LOADED
description: Relo is the first fully autonomous token powered and managed entirely by artificial intelligence — no human intervention, no emotional bias. Its ecosystem evolves on its own through advanced algorithms that learn, adapt, and improve over time. A massive and passionate community contributes daily with ideas, feedback, and innovation, making Relo smarter, faster, and more effective with every interaction. This is not just a project — it’s the birth of true AI-driven autonomy in crypto.
